overview.en: Launched on Sept. 26, 2019 by the SMATOOS HONGKONG company, BeNative Digital Voucher can be used to subscribe for BeNative Service. BeNative is a global online English learning service offered to members of 181 countries around the world since 2016. BeNative Digital Vouchers are designed to motivate people to learn through rewards. It overcomes the problem of high fees for small international payments for BeNative subscriptions and rewards
